OOC: Oh god! thanks for reminding me earth!

::The Destrocons wake up, but something is not right.  There quarters were in 
the part of the ship that was not destroyed, so he doesnt know yet::
Ramjet: Theres something... strange about this place tonight...
::They walk further.  They come to the wrecked part of the ship.  They see 
Gravedigger::
Skywarp: My god.
Dirge: He had much fear when he died-
Ramjet: Shut up!  We should look for survivors.
::They start walking around the base::
Skywarp:  Is anyone alive out there?
